text: Alejandro Orózco (born 12 February 1965) is a Mexican equestrian. He competed in the individual jumping event at the 1988 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1965 births Category:Living people Category:Mexican male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Mexico Category:Equestrians at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
